examples.en: We have been flooded with responses to our advertisement.
His responses have slowed with age.
At the last count, I had 15 responses to my letter.
The editorial unleashed a torrent of angry responses.
There is a great deal of variation among the responses.
Compartment the responses according to country of origin.
Emotional responses are a function of the right hemisphere of the brain.
Responses to the individual items are scored on a scale ranging from 0 to 12.
Their customer service department always gives courteous responses, even to rude people.
